Darling Légitimus https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Darling_L%C3%A9gitimus 0 Mathilda Marie Berthilde Paruta (21 November 1907 – 7 December 1999), better known as Darling Légitimus, was a French actress. In 1983, she received the Volpi Cup for Best Actress for her performance in the film Sugar Cane Alley.
